parameters: Once a good for location for Bladesville to mine all
of its ore, it's now completely overrun with monsters.
The people of Bladesville now have to mine elsewhere,
which makes everything a lot more inconvenient.
Those who can brave the slimes and undead creatures
inside will be rewarded with many types of ore.
Going further in unprepared may very well be the
end of you! Proceed with caution!
